<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error 404 - Página no encontrada</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f0f0f5;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 8rem;
            color: #ff6b6b;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #ff6b6b;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #e55a5a;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <p>¡Oops! La página que buscas no se encuentra.</p>
        <p>Intenta volver a la <a href="/">página principal</a>.</p>
    </div>
    </body>
    </html>